Token.Abstract: The delegate for a nomadPOS app. nomadPOSIOSAppDelegate is the application delegate responsible for creating and configuring the nomadPOS app's root view controller and the navigation controller that will contain it. It supports additional networking functionality by providing methods for detecting wifi/gsm connectivity and events for responding to changes in that connectivity.
